Fleetmatics Group PLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 4:31 PM ET
Software

Company Overview of Fleetmatics Group PLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Fleetmatics Group PLC provides software-as-a-service mobile workforce solutions for small and medium-sized businesses (SMBs) worldwide. The company offers Web-based and mobile application solutions that offer fleet operators with visibility into vehicle location, fuel usage, speed and mileage, and other insights into their mobile workforce. It provides cloud-based software solutions for service businesses and their mobile workers; Fleetmatics REVEAL, a business-intelligence based fleet management solution for SMBs; Fleetmatics REVEAL+ solution to large enterprise customers; Fleetmatics WORK, a field service management solution; and Routist, an intelligent vehicle routing solution for busines...
Fleetmatics Group PLC provides software-as-a-service mobile workforce solutions for small and medium-sized businesses (SMBs) worldwide. The company offers Web-based and mobile application solutions that offer fleet operators with visibility into vehicle location, fuel usage, speed and mileage, and other insights into their mobile workforce. It provides cloud-based software solutions for service businesses and their mobile workers; Fleetmatics REVEAL, a business-intelligence based fleet management solution for SMBs; Fleetmatics REVEAL+ solution to large enterprise customers; Fleetmatics WORK, a field service management solution; and Routist, an intelligent vehicle routing solution for businesses. The company sells its products primarily through its direct sales organization and Web. Fleetmatics Group PLC was founded in 2004 and is based in Tallaght, Ireland. As of November 7, 2016, Fleetmatics Group PLC operates as a subsidiary of Verizon Communications Inc.
Detailed Description


