GPS Tracking App: Carry Your Fleet in Your Pocket


See what the Fleetmatics REVEAL tracking app can do for you
When business doesn’t stop, you don’t stop. With our fleet management app, you can access key information about your team from anywhere, anytime. 


 
Available for Android®, iPhone™, and iPad™ 
















Our Native App
With the easy-to-use Fleetmatics App, get the visibility you’ve been dreaming of, right in the palm of your hand.









Get full functionality with the tracking app so you can:

Access the dashboard, live map, reports, alerts and more 
Find the closest vehicles for urgent dispatch 
View animated vehicle journeys in route replay 
Display Geofences on a map 
Send a stop to a Garmin device 

All with full-function native applications, not just a map in a web browser.  



 


FREE DEMO
                




















































